                    {
                        text: "Warning signs include sharper heel pain during exercise, worse first-step pain the next morning, or a week-on-week upward trend in symptoms. Mild muscle fatigue in the calf is fine; sharp pain at the heel is not. If symptoms flare, hold your current level for a week or step back to ",
